26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_sw_nv04.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#define nv04_sw_chan(p) container_of((p), struct nv04_sw_chan, base)
30#include "priv.h"
31#include "chan.h"
32#include "nvsw.h"
33
34#include <nvif/class.h>
35#include <nvif/ioctl.h>
36#include <nvif/unpack.h>
37
38struct nv04_sw_chan {
39 struct nvkm_sw_chan base;
40 atomic_t ref;
41};
42
43/*******************************************************************************
44 * software object classes
45 ******************************************************************************/
46
47static int
48nv04_nvsw_mthd_get_ref(struct nvkm_nvsw *nvsw, void *data, u32 size)
49{
50 struct nv04_sw_chan *chan = nv04_sw_chan(nvsw->chan);
51 union {
52 struct nv04_nvsw_get_ref_v0 v0;
53 } *args = data;
54 int ret;
55
56 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
57 args->v0.ref = atomic_read(&chan->ref);
58 }
59
60 return ret;
61}
62
63static int
64nv04_nvsw_mthd(struct nvkm_nvsw *nvsw, u32 mthd, void *data, u32 size)
65{
66 switch (mthd) {
67 case NV04_NVSW_GET_REF:
68 return nv04_nvsw_mthd_get_ref(nvsw, data, size);
69 default:
70 break;
71 }
72 return -EINVAL;
73}
74
75static const struct nvkm_nvsw_func
76nv04_nvsw = {
77 .mthd = nv04_nvsw_mthd,
78};
79
80static int
81nv04_nvsw_new(struct nvkm_sw_chan *chan, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
82 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
83{
84 return nvkm_nvsw_new_(&nv04_nvsw, chan, oclass, data, size, pobject);
85}
86
87/*******************************************************************************
88 * software context
89 ******************************************************************************/
90
91static bool
92nv04_sw_chan_mthd(struct nvkm_sw_chan *base, int subc, u32 mthd, u32 data)
93{
94 struct nv04_sw_chan *chan = nv04_sw_chan(base);
95
96 switch (mthd) {
97 case 0x0150:
98 atomic_set(&chan->ref, data);
99 return true;
100 default:
101 break;
102 }
103
104 return false;
105}
106
107static const struct nvkm_sw_chan_func
108nv04_sw_chan = {
109 .mthd = nv04_sw_chan_mthd,
110};
111
112static int
113nv04_sw_chan_new(struct nvkm_sw *sw, struct nvkm_fifo_chan *fifo,
114 const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
115{
116 struct nv04_sw_chan *chan;
117
118 if (!(chan = kzalloc(sizeof(*chan), GFP_KERNEL)))
119 return -ENOMEM;
120 atomic_set(&chan->ref, 0);
121 *pobject = &chan->base.object;
122
123 return nvkm_sw_chan_ctor(&nv04_sw_chan, sw, fifo, oclass, &chan->base);
124}
125
126/*******************************************************************************
127 * software engine/subdev functions
128 ******************************************************************************/
129
130static const struct nvkm_sw_func
131nv04_sw = {
132 .chan_new = nv04_sw_chan_new,
133 .sclass = {
134 { nv04_nvsw_new, { -1, -1, NVIF_IOCTL_NEW_V0_SW_NV04 } },
135 {}
136 }
137};
138
139int
140nv04_sw_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_sw **psw)
141{
142 return nvkm_sw_new_(&nv04_sw, device, index, psw);
143}
